{"tha-ap80:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap80:0.2":"Nagasamalavagga ","tha-ap80:0.3":"Patalipupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap80:1.1":"“Suvannavannam sambuddham, ","tha-ap80:1.2":"Gacchantam antarapane; ","tha-ap80:1.3":"Kancanagghiyasankasam, ","tha-ap80:1.4":"Battimsavaralakkhanam. ","tha-ap80:2.1":"Setthiputto tada asim, ","tha-ap80:2.2":"sukhumalo sukhedhito; ","tha-ap80:2.3":"Ucchange patalipuppham, ","tha-ap80:2.4":"katvana abhisamharim. ","tha-ap80:3.1":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap80:3.2":"pupphehi abhipujayim; ","tha-ap80:3.3":"Tissam lokavidum natham, ","tha-ap80:3.4":"naradevam namassaham. ","tha-ap80:4.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap80:4.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap80:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap80:4.4":"pupphapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap80:5.1":"Ito tesatthikappamhi, ","tha-ap80:5.2":"abhisammatanamako; ","tha-ap80:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap80:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap80:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap80:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap80:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap80:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma patalipupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap80:8.1":"Patalipupphiyattherassapadanam atthamam. "}